Amazon.com - 'Walking The Line' is a collection of recordings from one of the most influential figures in music history, Johnny Cash. Culled from the vaults of the legendary Sun Records, this 3-disc set documents Cash's most prolific period as a songwriter, and is the perfect showcase for his dark country stylings and dry, witty lyrics. Includes the tracks 'I Walk The Line', 'Give My Love To Rose' and 'Folsom Prison Blues'.
